branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The SRF30 series is designed to regulate DI water and N2 gas in the clean room. Fluoro resin material is used in the fluid contact area. The fluid contact area is washed with freon ultra sonic and DI water.
&lt;/p&gt;

